OL,3,CPolice force reprimanded over loss of
OL,4,C96,000 pieces of bodycam video
OL,6,FA police force has been formally
OL,7,Freprimanded after accidentally
OL,8,Fdeleting more than 96,000 pieces of
OL,9,Fbody worn camera evidence.
OL,11,FThe Information Commissioner's Office
OL,12,F(ICO) said South Yorkshire Police
OL,13,Flacked the "appropriate technical and
OL,14,Forganisational measures in place to
OL,15,Fkeep the evidence secure".
OL,17,FThe force revealed in 2023 it had lost
OL,18,Ffootage from cameras worn by officers
OL,19,Fspanning a three-year period.
