OL,3,CPolice force reprimanded over loss of
OL,4,C96,000 pieces of bodycam video
OL,6,FThe ICO's investigation found 96,174
OL,7,Fpieces of footage recorded between
OL,8,FJuly 2020 and May 2023 had been
OL,9,Fmistakenly deleted on 26 July 2023.
OL,11,FThe data related to 126 criminal
OL,12,Fcases, but only three were impacted by
OL,13,Fthe loss.
OL,15,FThe ICO's head of investigations Sally
OL,16,FAnne Poole said: "This incident
OL,17,Fhighlights the importance of having
OL,18,Fdetailed policies and procedures in
OL,19,Fplace to mitigate against the loss of
OL,20,Fevidence.
