OL,3,CPolice force reprimanded over loss of
OL,4,C96,000 pieces of bodycam video
OL,6,F"People rightly have high expectations
OL,7,Fthat our police forces and services,
OL,8,Fwhich protect us, also protect the
OL,9,Fpersonal information they hold."
OL,11,FThe IOC's investigation found the loss
OL,12,Fhappened after a system upgrade in May
OL,13,F2023, which caused the secure system
OL,14,Fto struggle with processing the
OL,15,Ffootage.
OL,17,FIt said South Yorkshire Police had
OL,18,Ffailed to introduce backup policies
OL,19,Ffor its data and had not escalated to
OL,20,Fsenior management when flaws were
OL,21,Fdiscovered in 2019.
