OL,3,CPolice force reprimanded over loss of
OL,4,C96,000 pieces of bodycam video
OL,6,F"Poor record keeping" meant it could
OL,7,Fnot confirm how many pieces of footage
OL,8,Fwere permanently lost.
OL,10,FIn a statement South Yorkshire Police
OL,11,Fsaid that the victims involved in the
OL,12,Faffected proceedings were informed and
OL,13,Fthat the force worked with the Crown
OL,14,FProsecution Service to reduce the
OL,15,Fimpact on the three affected cases,
OL,16,Fwhich comprised of two assaults
OL,17,Fagainst police officers and one affray.
