OL,6,FDeputy Chief Constable Sarah Poolman
OL,7,Fsaid: "We do not underestimate the
OL,8,Fdamage any loss of data can do to our
OL,9,Fcommunities' trust and confidence in
OL,10,Fus.
OL,12,F"Whilst the Information Commissioner's
OL,13,FOffice has welcomed the steps taken by
OL,14,Fus in the immediate aftermath, such as
OL,15,Ftrying to retrieve the footage and
OL,16,Finforming those affected, we are sorry
OL,17,Fthat any victim of crime faced this
OL,18,Fchallenge whilst going through the
OL,19,Fcriminal justice system.
